{"tid":912892,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"不明來歷嘅奇怪和尚","createTime":"2018-11-23T04:21:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-23T10:32:41.000Z","uid":205645,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"be9d09b9e15f7a2d96a1dfbc2c46f77091353782","tid":912892,"uid":205645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T04:21:02.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n我今日返屋企嗰陣<br />\n見到屋企附近嚟咗個和尚<br />\n個和尚戴住墨鏡<br />\n坐住電動輪椅輪椅<br />\n當我打算經過嗰陣<br />\n個和尚突然間起身行埋嚟<br />\n佢自稱太虛湯馬士<br />\n和尚: 你嚮往西方極樂世界嗎?<br />\n我同佢講: <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個和尚突然間坐返落電動輪椅<br />\n拎咗個不知從哪來嘅木魚出嚟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有本封面寫住「摩訶般若波羅蜜大明咒經」嘅經書<br />\n諗住渡化我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當佢一打開本經書<br />\n原來入面係Thomas故事書<br />\n心知不妙嘅我當然即刻走<br />\n結果個和尚坐住電動輪椅開住本Thomas故事書敲住木魚飛馳喺市區追住我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n「觀世音菩薩，行深般若波羅蜜時，照見五陰空，度一切苦厄。舍利弗！&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n佢一路念一路追咗我5條街<br />\n<br />\n到底點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"587258930aceec90e6cd84ff6347f1c03f7536c0","tid":912892,"uid":28031,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T04:22:14.000Z","msg":"3/10<br />\n<br />\n虎頭蛇尾"},{"pid":"0892534e317c6f9bc7b21849fb87922121eef6ea","tid":912892,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T04:27:10.000Z","msg":"我佛你"},{"pid":"ef3ce69ee07125429ea9ec166f81b00bf1182716","tid":912892,"uid":92230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T04:33:06.000Z","msg":"2/10<br />\n故事多有伏筆 惜結尾未能清楚交代 下次宜先寫好故事骨架重點 後開始寫作"},{"pid":"7bae7fd4357019f0adf39cdec004dbd8c9bb6b1c","tid":912892,"uid":205645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0892534e317c6f9bc7b21849fb87922121eef6ea","tid":912892,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T04:27:10.000Z","msg":"我佛你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T05:28:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34a259108b83868ac8884e3e69fd3b0e90d872c7","tid":912892,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T05:51:16.000Z","msg":"裝返個奶同淫僧針針先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bce2faddeea1e45a83f1c48f1108a3a97507071","tid":912892,"uid":158372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T10:32:41.000Z","msg":"墨你老母鏡"}]}